Trade/Device Name(s): FORA Premium V10 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
FORA Premium V10 Blood Glucose Meter
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): FORA Premium V10 Blood Glucose Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for FORA Premium V10 Blood Glucose Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose using electrochemical biosensor technology.
Indications for Use Summary: For quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from finger and alternative sites to aid in monitoring diabetes control at home by a single user; not for diagnosis or screening of diabetes, neonates, or visually impaired.
